{"tid":258703,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求知慾] 學英文","createTime":"2017-05-26T10:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T13:36:20.000Z","uid":82408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"572e86d9e01dce55fa8b6ec810adfee7a7051532","tid":258703,"uid":82408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小弟周不時都有d英文唔明點用 希望連登有心人士可以分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日睇報紙見人用<strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">With </span></strong></strong></strong>做開頭 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>With </strong></span>so many English-language print titles owned by one large media group,xxxx <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>With </strong></span>so many media titles already run by or controlled by Beijing, xxxxx<br />\n<br />\n但係上網search with放係句首用法又唔係好清楚<br />\n<br />\n所以上黎求問 想學識點運用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該"},{"pid":"150148465a8398d386ac6855d10eef0901576325","tid":258703,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"咪即係解當有xxx,就會yyy咁<br />\nE.g. With me, lihkg can prosper"},{"pid":"86ec258db9d8831ca6b37de434677a5720b1a7df","tid":258703,"uid":82408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪即係解當有xxx,就會yyy咁<br />\nE.g. With me, lihkg can prosper</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係解 &quot;當有&quot; = With?"},{"pid":"316e11b710fd266c2ef008279a32c4b1927b8f8a","tid":258703,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪即係解當有xxx,就會yyy咁<br />\nE.g. With me, lihkg can prosper</blockquote><br />\n你嗰語法邏輯啱,with + noun, 但係conventionally(「傳統上」)唔會咁樣寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用返Because of me應該會合乎規範多啲。<br />\n姐係好似「恭喜發財」同「恭喜發達」,一般人都應該會明「恭喜發達」嗰意思,但係日常用法唔會係講「恭喜發達」"},{"pid":"8533f5cdfedbf7744f093a6997f1dbcdb56cd374","tid":258703,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪即係解當有xxx,就會yyy咁<br />\nE.g. With me, lihkg can prosper</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係解 &quot;當有&quot; = With?</blockquote><br />\n其實英文直接翻譯中文有佢嘅limitation,不過學習有時都無可厚非嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係要譯,我會譯「憑藉」。"},{"pid":"91231cbe2f2e220ab8d6bb1d338cf197e457ca33","tid":258703,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"其實呢d睇得多就get到個意思<br />\n樓主可以試下作下句子post上黎睇下用得啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435bfe215047bbb3bfdd762a495ae536078aabd3","tid":258703,"uid":100971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我都研究過<br />\nwith 咁用通常表示因果關係 (原因assume大家都知)<br />\n但係就咁接一個單丁名詞硬係怪怪地<br />\nwith me, ...<br />\n通常好聽D係接non-finite clause, 例如你果兩句"}]}